'''John Hazlett''' wrote the article "[[The Written Word]]" for [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]], and the backstory of [[Cane Adiss/Legends|Cane Adiss]] and [[Slyther Bushforb/Legends|Slyther Bushforb]], both appearing in the [[Databank (original)|Databank]], through the ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of Hyperspace. Also, ''[[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]]'' author [[Abel G. Peña]] thanked Hazlett for his suggestions regarding the book.<ref name="Abel">{{Blog|abelgpena|99|Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide}}</ref>

Hazlett's alias is ''{{U|jSarek}}'' on [[StarWars.com]], [[TheForce.net]]'s [[Jedi Council Forums]], and [[Wookieepedia]]. On the last, he was once an administrator and bureaucrat.

